ure, the analogous result is obtained for the\nsubalgebra of K\\\"ahler Weyl curvature tensors. It is shown that the\nanti-self-dual Weyl tensors on a four-dimensional vector space form a simple\nfive-dimensional ideal isometrically isomorphic to the trace-free part of the\nJordan product on trace-free $3 \\times 3$ symmetric matrices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Jan 2019 16:24:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Jan 2019 14:21:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 14 Mar 2019 10:56:24 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 11:31:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-13"}
