ucing higher dimensional---U(N) coin operations in\nthe modified SS-DQW we can include non-abelian potentials in the same DH. In\norder to simulate two-particle DH in presence of curved space-time and external\npotentials, we have used two particle modified SS-DQW, where the shift\noperations act separately on each particle, the coin operations which act\nsimultaneously on both particles contain all kinds of interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Jan 2019 16:37:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-15"}
