stances. We discuss the implications of this result, and underline the\npotential constraining power of CGM observations - in emission and absorption -\non galactic outflow models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 13 Jan 2019 16:46:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-23"}
