tion with superior performance relative to channel\nestimation is attainable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2019 04:03:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2019 03:33:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-19"}
